\subsection{Pros and Cons of Architecture}

\textbf{Pros}:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Modularity: Easy to develop, test, and maintain individual components
    \item Scalability: Horizontal scaling of individual services
    \item Technology Flexibility: Different services can use different technologies
    \item Resilience: Failure in one service doesn't bring down entire system
    \item Team Scalability: Different teams can work on different services
\end{itemize}

\textbf{Cons}:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Complexity: More moving parts to manage and deploy
    \item Network Latency: Inter-service communication overhead
    \item Data Consistency: Distributed transactions are complex
    \item Debugging Difficulty: Tracing requests across multiple services
    \item Operational Overhead: More infrastructure to manage
\end{itemize}

